the course is created by the Coursera project network and takes about 2 hours to complete. In this project, Canva is used as a platform for working on this project and has three structures: Course Overview: This introductory reading material, five integrated projects and one quiz consisting of 5 questions. This project resulted in 5 integrated projects: Create a Course Promo Graphic, Create a Course Checklist, Create a Fillable PDF, Create a Worksheet for a Digital Course, and Create a Course Certificate for a Digital Course. This course makes it easy for me to carry out the training provided by Coursera by adding a video tutorial. There are subtitles in English to help my understanding when working on this course and the material presented by the teacher. In addition, the video tutorials displayed follow the training assignments given. This course helps me to explore more about the designs that are trending at the moment. In my opinion, this course is easy to do and understand for a novice user like me.
